{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781756717030,"sessionID":"ses_1270761e3ffewfNQvkGMF3JgBO","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_c55f6N0HjttItu0ZpdRof1Bm","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/020-maintenance-grace-background-embedding/graph-metadata.json","offset":1,"limit":1000},"output":"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/020-maintenance-grace-background-embedding/graph-metadata.json</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\n2:   \"schema_version\": 1,\n3:   \"packet_id\": \"system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/020-maintenance-grace-background-embedding\",\n4:   \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/020-maintenance-grace-background-embedding\",\n5:   \"parent_id\": \"system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search\",\n6:   \"children_ids\": [],\n7:   \"manual\": {\n8:     \"depends_on\": [],\n9:     \"supersedes\": [],\n10:     \"related_to\": []\n11:   },\n12:   \"derived\": {\n13:     \"trigger_phrases\": [\n14:       \"maintenance grace background embedding\",\n15:       \"maintenance marker reference counted embedding queue\",\n16:       \"reindex post-scan embedding burst re-election\",\n17:       \"027 002/020\",\n18:       \"maintenance grace background embedding plan\",\n19:       \"reference-counted marker embedding queue plan\",\n20:       \"027 002/020 plan\",\n21:       \"maintenance grace background embedding tasks\",\n22:       \"027 002/020 tasks\",\n23:       \"maintenance grace background embedding summary\",\n24:       \"reference-counted marker embedding queue shipped\",\n25:       \"027 002/020 shipped\"\n26:     ],\n27:     \"key_topics\": [\n28:       \"maintenance\",\n29:       \"grace\",\n30:       \"background\",\n31:       \"embedding\",\n32:       \"marker\",\n33:       \"reference\",\n34:       \"counted\",\n35:       \"queue\",\n36:       \"reindex\",\n37:       \"post-scan\",\n38:       \"burst\",\n39:       \"re-election\"\n40:     ],\n41:     \"importance_tier\": \"normal\",\n42:     \"status\": \"complete_(code)\",\n43:     \"key_files\": [\n44:       \"lib/providers/retry-manager.ts\",\n45:       \"lib/storage/maintenance-marker.ts\",\n46:       \"handlers/memory-index.ts\",\n47:       \"tests/maintenance-marker.vitest.ts\",\n48:       \"mcp_server/lib/storage/maintenance-marker.ts\",\n49:       \"mcp_server/handlers/memory-index.ts\",\n50:       \"mcp_server/lib/providers/retry-manager.ts\",\n51:       \"mcp_server/tests/maintenance-marker.vitest.ts\",\n52:       \"spec.md\",\n53:       \"plan.md\",\n54:       \"implementation-summary.md\",\n55:       \"tasks.md\"\n56:     ],\n57:     \"entities\": [\n58:       {\n59:         \"name\": \"retry-manager.ts\",\n60:         \"kind\": \"code\",\n61:         \"path\": \"lib/providers/retry-manager.ts\",\n62:         \"source\": \"derived\"\n63:       },\n64:       {\n65:         \"name\": \"maintenance-marker.ts\",\n66:         \"kind\": \"code\",\n67:         \"path\": \"lib/storage/maintenance-marker.ts\",\n68:         \"source\": \"derived\"\n69:       },\n70:       {\n71:         \"name\": \"memory-index.ts\",\n72:         \"kind\": \"code\",\n73:         \"path\": \"handlers/memory-index.ts\",\n74:         \"source\": \"derived\"\n75:       },\n76:       {\n77:         \"name\": \"maintenance-marker.vitest.ts\",\n78:         \"kind\": \"test\",\n79:         \"path\": \"tests/maintenance-marker.vitest.ts\",\n80:         \"source\": \"derived\"\n81:       },\n82:       {\n83:         \"name\": \"spec.md\",\n84:         \"kind\": \"doc\",\n85:         \"path\": \"spec.md\",\n86:         \"source\": \"derived\"\n87:       },\n88:       {\n89:         \"name\": \"plan.md\",\n90:         \"kind\": \"doc\",\n91:         \"path\": \"plan.md\",\n92:         \"source\": \"derived\"\n93:       },\n94:       {\n95:         \"name\": \"implementation-summary.md\",\n96:         \"kind\": \"doc\",\n97:         \"path\": \"implementation-summary.md\",\n98:         \"source\": \"derived\"\n99:       },\n100:       {\n101:         \"name\": \"tasks.md\",\n102:         \"kind\": \"doc\",\n103:         \"path\": \"tasks.md\",\n104:         \"source\": \"derived\"\n105:       },\n106:       {\n107:         \"name\": \"Feature Specification\",\n108:         \"kind\": \"proper_noun\",\n109:         \"path\": \"spec.md\",\n110:         \"source\": \"derived\"\n111:       },\n112:       {\n113:         \"name\": \"Parent Spec\",\n114:         \"kind\": \"proper_noun\",\n115:         \"path\": \"spec.md\",\n116:         \"source\": \"derived\"\n117:       },\n118:       {\n119:         \"name\": \"Handoff Criteria\",\n120:         \"kind\": \"proper_noun\",\n121:         \"path\": \"spec.md\",\n122:         \"source\": \"derived\"\n123:       },\n124:       {\n125:         \"name\": \"Phase Context This\",\n126:         \"kind\": \"proper_noun\",\n127:         \"path\": \"spec.md\",\n128:         \"source\": \"derived\"\n129:       },\n130:       {\n131:         \"name\": \"Scope Boundary\",\n132:         \"kind\": \"proper_noun\",\n133:         \"path\": \"spec.md\",\n134:         \"source\": \"derived\"\n135:       },\n136:       {\n137:         \"name\": \"Problem Statement\",\n138:         \"kind\": \"proper_noun\",\n139:         \"path\": \"spec.md\",\n140:         \"source\": \"derived\"\n141:       },\n142:       {\n143:         \"name\": \"Implementation Plan\",\n144:         \"kind\": \"proper_noun\",\n145:         \"path\": \"plan.md\",\n146:         \"source\": \"derived\"\n147:       },\n148:       {\n149:         \"name\": \"Uses Node\",\n150:         \"kind\": \"proper_noun\",\n151:         \"path\": \"plan.md\",\n152:         \"source\": \"derived\"\n153:       },\n154:       {\n155:         \"name\": \"a\",\n156:         \"kind\": \"key_phrase\",\n157:         \"path\": \"plan.md\",\n158:         \"source\": \"derived\"\n159:       },\n160:       {\n161:         \"name\": \"the\",\n162:         \"kind\": \"key_phrase\",\n163:         \"path\": \"plan.md\",\n164:         \"source\": \"derived\"\n165:       },\n166:       {\n167:         \"name\": \"no\",\n168:         \"kind\": \"key_phrase\",\n169:         \"path\": \"plan.md\",\n170:         \"source\": \"derived\"\n171:       },\n172:       {\n173:         \"name\": \"1. SUMMARY\",\n174:         \"kind\": \"heading\",\n175:         \"path\": \"plan.md\",\n176:         \"source\": \"derived\"\n177:       },\n178:       {\n179:         \"name\": \"Task Format\",\n180:         \"kind\": \"proper_noun\",\n181:         \"path\": \"tasks.md\",\n182:         \"source\": \"derived\"\n183:       },\n184:       {\n185:         \"name\": \"Task Notation\",\n186:         \"kind\": \"proper_noun\",\n187:         \"path\": \"tasks.md\",\n188:         \"source\": \"derived\"\n189:       },\n190:       {\n191:         \"name\": \"Completion Criteria The\",\n192:         \"kind\": \"proper_noun\",\n193:         \"path\": \"tasks.md\",\n194:         \"source\": \"derived\"\n195:       },\n196:       {\n197:         \"name\": \"Phase 1: Setup\",\n198:         \"kind\": \"heading\",\n199:         \"path\": \"tasks.md\",\n200:         \"source\": \"derived\"\n201:       }\n202:     ],\n203:     \"causal_summary\": \"This phase is the direct follow-on to 019. 019 made a reindex's SCAN survive launcher re-election by writing a maintenance-active marker that the launcher reads to adopt a busy-but-healthy daemon instead of reaping it. But that marker was scoped to the scan job. Because the scan defers embeddings (`asyncEmbedding`), the real vector writes happen AFTER the scan, in the background-embedding queue (`lib/providers/retry-manager.ts` draining `embedding_status='pending'` rows). That queue is busy-but-unprotected: a live run saw a separate re-election recycle the daemon DURING the post-scan embedding burst, interrupting the embeddings. Search stayed up and the gap drained on a later queue pass, but the reindex was not re-election-proof end to end. 019's own limitations section flagged this as the loop-closing follow-on.\",\n204:     \"created_at\": \"2026-06-17T13:56:34.988Z\",\n205:     \"last_save_at\": \"2026-06-17T13:56:34.988Z\",\n206:     \"save_lineage\": \"same_pass\",\n207:     \"last_accessed_at\": null,\n208:     \"source_docs\": [\n209:       \"spec.md\",\n210:       \"plan.md\",\n211:       \"tasks.md\",\n212:       \"implementation-summary.md\"\n213:     ],\n214:     \"last_active_child_id\": null,\n215:     \"last_active_at\": null\n216:   }\n217: }\n\n(End of file - total 217 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\n  \"schema_version\": 1,\n  \"packet_id\": \"system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/020-maintenance-grace-background-embedding\",\n  \"spec_folder\": \"system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/020-maintenance-grace-background-embedding\",\n  \"parent_id\": \"system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search\",\n  \"children_ids\": [],\n  \"manual\": {\n    \"depends_on\": [],\n    \"supersedes\": [],\n    \"related_to\": []\n  },\n  \"derived\": {\n    \"trigger_phrases\": [\n      \"maintenance grace background embedding\",\n      \"maintenance marker reference counted embedding queue\",\n      \"reindex post-scan embedding burst re-election\",\n      \"027 002/020\",\n      \"maintenance grace background embedding plan\",\n      \"reference-counted marker embedding queue plan\",\n      \"027 002/020 plan\",","truncated":false,"loaded":[],"display":{"type":"file","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Envi